# 📝 Note App Website

A responsive and interactive Note Application built using HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, and Vanilla JavaScript.

## 🚀 Features
- Loading ....
- Add new notes with title and content
- Save notes permanently using localStorage
- Track editing state using sessionStorage
- Delete individual notes
- Clear all notes
- Search and filter notes dynamically
- Sort notes (Newest to Oldest / Oldest to Newest)
- Confirmation modal for unsaved changes
- Smooth UI animations and overlay effects
- Responsive design

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Bootstrap 5
- JavaScript (ES6)
- LocalStorage
- SessionStorage

## 💡 Project Purpose

This project was built to practice DOM manipulation, storage handling, form validation, and UI/UX improvements using JavaScript.

